== Naming ==

I wonder if the Austro-Hungarian name might be a better title for this article - the bulk of the article is about the ship's service in WWI - 4 and a half years - and the section that deals with her career as ''Morava'' primarily covers about a week and a half in April 1941. [[User:Parsecboy|Parsecboy]] ([[User talk:Parsecboy|talk]]) 21:55, 27 February 2015 (UTC)
