== Photo ==

There's a photo of the vessel [http://www.history.navy.mil/our-collections/photography/numerical-list-of-images/nhhc-series/nh-series/NH-88000/NH-88921.html here] that should be usable. [[User:Parsecboy|Parsecboy]] ([[User talk:Parsecboy|talk]]) 21:10, 7 January 2016 (UTC)

Yes. Since it seems to have been adopted in the article, and since the article is now a featured article, I have updated the description page of the photo in question (which appeared on a postcard of the time) to reflect the correct name of the painter (not Hausser, but Heusser, a very well known painter of seascapes and sea battles). [[Special:Contributions/122.58.35.27|122.58.35.27]] ([[User talk:122.58.35.27|talk]])
